name: hyperfine
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.14.0" %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: hyperfine
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/sharkdp/hyperfine/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 59018c22242dd2ad2bd5fb4a34c0524948b7921d02aa79419ccec4c1ffd3da14

build:
  number: 0

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('rust') }}
    - {{ compiler('c') }}   # [unix]
    - {{ native }}binutils    # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - hyperfine --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/sharkdp/hyperfine
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  summary: A command-line benchmarking tool
  license_file: LICENSE-MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dbast
